Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:05.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess Recovery Battle has ended peacefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:08.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's worth a celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing is that the princess's concert went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:16.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, it'll be happily ever after.\NAt least, I'd love it if that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:18.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:12.90,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(800,0)\pos(217,359)}  「Star Reading Princess 」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:12.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Myon Castle Battle and the princess's concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:16.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Galette Army that had previously remained
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,has begun to back out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:25.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And here, at an audience with the princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:27.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knights of Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:30.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,None of you gave up despite our continuous losses in the battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:34.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so the credit of our victory goes to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:38.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us proceed with the award presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:42.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader of the Knights, Laurent \NMartinozzi, please come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:47.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're actually doing this ceremony in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:51.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero, what kind of a country did you think we were?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a national affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:55.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course everything needs to be done orderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:02.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Imperial Guards, Lady Eclair Martinozzi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:03.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:11.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair, thank you for taking care of our hero on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:15.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were also the first person who came to save me just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Eclair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:23.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm honored by your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair is ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:30.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's a great honor to be patted by the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:33.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:42.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a few days since Sir Hero came to Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:53.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sir Hero and Rico. Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:56.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disturb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. It's the usual clippings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:02.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and there's something extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:08.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we have refreshments for the knights, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you help us deliver it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:13.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also a share for the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:20.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's refreshment is flower honey flavored tart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:25.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Rico, or even girls in general,\Nreally do have a sweet tooth, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:29.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not just an ordinary girl. I use my brain a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:32.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need all the sugar I can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero and the chief are delivering this personally?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:46.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:47.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, the kitchen has provided refreshments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have refreshments!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm all right. I don't need any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to practice a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:05.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, then why don't I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:10.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero, can you assist her once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:11.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:16.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero and the Captain of the\NImperial Guards will be fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:17.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:21.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What weapon are you going to use today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Show off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:41.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair seems to be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it doesn't seem right to compliment my sister this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:07.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there haven't been any young knights at her skill level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's found someone on par with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's a good thing for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're about the same age, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be great to have Sir Hero as my brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:36.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt a bad, chilly feeling just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I didn't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you've caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:44.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You do look like the kind who would reveal her stomach while sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O... Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:58.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You dumb hero! Don't touch a knight's forehead so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! You perverted hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:04.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like they get along well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What misfortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Eclair overreacted?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:23.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. Doggies, please lead the way. {dogs in a human dog world? what kind of evolution is this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:39.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:48.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady d'Arquien, good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is a good day to fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:56.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Biscotti was also in a period of uncertainty,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:08:00.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we finished our hunt early and came back as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like we worried too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:07.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero and Eclair are doing so much, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:11.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sir Hero, you seem like a very interesting person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:17.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you just recently arrived in Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,yet the Knights, Rico,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the citizens have opened their hearts to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:26.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, though Eclair does kick and beat me up sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:30.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That must be her showing that she trusts you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be great if it were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've caught something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:40.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's big! It's a big catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be a big fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please cook that as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:11.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sir Hero, I heard you're from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:16.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that means you'll go back to your homeworld one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you like to stay here forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally forgot about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:28.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't found a way to return home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:30.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I just asked if you wanted to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:39.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes who answer the summon are \Nunable to return to their homeworlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:43.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though this is the traditional saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:48.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, in distant countries, there were stories \Nabout heroes returning after completing their missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:51.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:55.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Rico was investigating this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have a family back in your homeworld, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:05.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's my father, mother, some relatives and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:10.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like the fish is cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll serve it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me. I wonder how Becky's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:25.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca? Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:30.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have at least answered!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come help me buy some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:35.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you should really tidy up your room a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a mess in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:43.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you slack so much just because Sink isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This has got nothing to do with Sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, he'd start texting me in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly he stopped doing it. \NDoesn't he know I'll get worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:56.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's Sink, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:01.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be good if he was just outside \Nimmersing himself in his activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I haven't been checking my fortune lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:09.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, my star sign is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's neither a good sign nor a bad sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Sink's?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This week's worst?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible luck all the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Laurent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:34.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What has Sir Hero been doing the whole day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, about that question,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you seem to be repeating it day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:46.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he should be with Lady d'Arquien right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:51.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Brioche likes him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she does. The same is true of Yukikaze and the Omitsu Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:01.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, as soon as you're done with this afternoon's lesson, and dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:07.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have a good chat with the hero then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:12.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Leader of Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:15.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In fact, I've notified Sir Hero too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Laurent, Amelita!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's not keep Leader of Knights waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish these documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:32.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:38.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:40.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:44.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us, kindly let us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:52.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They stand out so much when they enter the city, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:56.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because they look as big as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:13:00.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll need to pay the Knight Army Headquarters a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you need to see the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:04.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:07.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to be polite to the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:08.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:18.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's have the princess's maidservant team wash Sir Hero from head to toe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:26.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been out the whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:32.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to ensure that you're worthy of appearing before the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:37.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Rizel Conchiglie, the head maid, will personally see to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:40.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can wash myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, Sir Hero has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:13.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit chilly today, so I've prepared some hot tea for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like sweet tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:17.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti's tea sure is tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells as good as fresh fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tea leaves are one of my country's proud products.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:30.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's known as a high-class item in other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um, Sir Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:39.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,allow me to apologize once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:42.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for summoning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:46.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:49.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has been really nice to me, and it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:52.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, haven't you heard from Rico?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:15:00.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like she's found a way for me to return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:08.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's something I would like to ask you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:09.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:12.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you choose me as the summoned hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:19.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, if it's a secret, then I won't ask again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:23.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not exactly a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:25.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:25.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about reading the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:30.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the crest techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:36.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see all sorts of things by using the image disc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All sorts of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that are outside the world, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:43.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Individually, you can search for things,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:45.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or you can look into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:49.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did say you could look, but you can't see very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:53.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you can see anything you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:54.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:59.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a thing or two about reading the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I try it once in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:04.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to see worlds that are far away from Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:09.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, there's a silver-colored battlefield that looks like a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A little boy was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:16.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a golden-haired boy who competed with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:25.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he was small, he had \Nreally swift and powerful moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:29.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried his very best and seemed really honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:34.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking how nice it'd be if he was my country's hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sir Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:44.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The me that you saw
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:47.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,must have been wearing a black shirt with a fire design, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was the competition that I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The war in my world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:58.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is known as a competition called "I Am Athletic."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:04.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who won was a pretty girl who's slightly older than you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. She's one of my relatives, and she's my master and rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:12.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You actually saw all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for spying on you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:18.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, it was on live telecast anyway, so I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to Nanami at the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I cried, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried so hard, yet I couldn't make it on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:30.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so upset because I couldn't catch up to that two seconds' distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if it was because I felt embarrassed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:35.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or because I let down my family and friends who came to support me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:39.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just cried and cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:45.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But those tears that you cried at that moment were beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:52.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were beautiful, precious tears that came from one who gave it his all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:58.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, compared to Nanami who won at the end, and all the other people, I feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:06.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh! No! I mean I just wanted to summon you as the hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:07.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, you can call me Sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir... Sink?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:23.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to everyone else, I wanted you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:28.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be good if Sink could be the hero of our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:40.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Lady d'Arquien.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to trouble you in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:48.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I've been out of the country during its worst moments for more than a year now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:51.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So if I can just help out with minor things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:55.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you weren't the kind to be tied down to a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:19:00.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, it's good enough that you can stay in Biscotti temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much of a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:06.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nothing but a wanderer. {or vagabond}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it that you'll be going east after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:18.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm looking for really depends on Yukikaze and the star readings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:21.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's really hard to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I'll try to stay a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:36.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I keep getting the feeling that our neighbor, the Galette Army, is up to no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:40.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Although I can't read the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:44.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's really obvious that the way \NGalette battles is simply abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:50.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking it's more Princess Leo instead of Galette itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As much as I don't want to think this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:00.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this could be related to the monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:05.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be my turn to join the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Sink,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:14.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,tomorrow morning's confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, six o'clock at that back door. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, are you going on a date with Sir Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:30.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him to join me on a morning walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:33.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink doesn't seem to have any problem waking up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're really looking forward to the morning walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Having morning walks together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:45.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I used to do that with Princess Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Yet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:00.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the war ended and I returned, nothing has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:03.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it became worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:09.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My star reading isn't supposed to be this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:10.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:13.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,why can I see the future so clearly now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:24.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,800)\an8}Princess Millhiore, owner of the Excellead, and Hero Sink, owner of the Palladion,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:27.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,600)\an8}will die in thirty days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:30.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,000)\an8}The future within this image disc will not change, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:34.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only Millhi, but even the Hero will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:36.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if this is fixed by the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:39.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like hell will I let this happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn, Clavel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're divine or from the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but as long as you exist, you can be changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:22:05.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo made a shocking proclamation to Biscotti and the other countries on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.17,0:23:52.27,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Maidservants! Do your thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:53.44,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes, ma'am!
